text:
we can do a ton of things in this new marketplace 

- lending items for rewards
- staking times for rewards 
- earning robux for completing tasks 
- earning robux for entering battles & simply playing the game

The reason why NFT’s play a role in Gaming 

Is because it puts our Limited Items on Roblox from Roblox’s hands to ours. 

Sure the items are in your inventory, but what if you get hacked? Or roblox bans you? 

Bye bye items !! 

With NFT integration this can’t happen as easy
